392
00:32:56,307 --> 00:32:59,392
If I'm together with Chigira-kun, I'm okay with anything.

393
00:33:15,201 --> 00:33:17,536
Stalking is not allowed today.

394
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:18,536
Eh?

395
00:33:19,163 --> 00:33:20,914
Come next to me.

396
00:33:21,666 --> 00:33:25,711
Well... but in the world of unrequited
love, this kind of thing never happens!

397
00:33:25,795 --> 00:33:28,296
This way is much more fun to climb.

398
00:33:30,049 --> 00:33:31,383
Chigira-kun.

399
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:36,846
