497
00:42:45,521 --> 00:42:49,649
But I can handle this alone.

498
00:42:52,152 --> 00:42:54,070
Are you avoiding me for some reason?

499
00:42:55,364 --> 00:42:56,447
No...

500
00:42:57,699 --> 00:43:00,117
