517
00:44:10,230 --> 00:44:11,772
Maybe on the rooftop?

518
00:44:15,819 --> 00:44:18,863
Maya, let's go to the chemistry lab.

519
00:44:18,947 --> 00:44:20,781
Yeah, let's go.

520
00:44:49,770 --> 00:44:51,062
