523
00:45:16,671 --> 00:45:19,298
That means how much you love...

524
00:45:21,009 --> 00:45:22,551
that person...

525
00:45:28,517 --> 00:45:29,642
But...

526
00:45:32,104 --> 00:45:34,397
If I admit my feelings...

527
00:45:40,153 --> 00:45:41,946
