00:47:45,320 --> 00:47:49,490
Don't we all become rational
stalkers when we're in love?

539
00:47:51,076 --> 00:47:52,993
This is definitely not stalking.

540
00:47:54,412 --> 00:47:56,330
Try to find me more seriously.

541
00:48:00,544 --> 00:48:01,627
Sui!

542
00:48:08,385 --> 00:48:10,678
Come to the rooftop when you're done,

543
00:48:10,762 --> 00:48:12,712
there's something I want to talk about.

544
00:48:12,931 --> 00:48:14,181
I'll be waiting.

545
00:48:14,641 --> 00:48:15,516
Okay.

546
00:48:32,826 --> 00:48:33,576
Maya.

547
00:48:33,660 --> 00:48:36,560
If you want to stop this
one-sided love game, just tell me.

548
00:48:37,038 --> 00:48:37,871
Huh?

549
00:48:37,998 --> 00:48:40,048
You look good together with Hanasaki-san.

550
00:48:40,250 --> 00:48:42,835
I support both of you.

551
00:48:49,092 --> 00:48:50,259
Are you okay?

552
00:48:50,760 --> 00:48:54,221
Yeah, it's fine. I'll go wash up a bit.

553
00:49:05,150 --> 00:49:07,109
I'll wash it.

554
00:49:07,193 --> 00:49:07,944
It's fine, it's fine!

555
00:49:08,028 --> 00:49:09,653
Chigira-kun, you can go back.

556
00:49:11,990 --> 00:49:12,907
Are you okay?

557
00:49:13,867 --> 00:49:15,693
I'm okay, I'm okay!

558
00:49:27,881 --> 00:49:29,006
Wear mine.

559
00:49:32,928 --> 00:49:35,512
If you don't, I'll have
you wear it by force.

560
00:49:42,312 --> 00:49:44,146
What am I doing?

561
00:49:48,026 --> 00:49:49,151
Miss Wizard!

562
00:49:54,449 --> 00:49:55,649
What's with that outfit?

563
00:49:56,117 --> 00:49:58,452
Um, this is...

564
00:50:08,588 --> 00:50:10,798
Is this blazer Chigira's?

565
00:50:20,392 --> 00:50:22,851
Miss Wizard, do you
like Chigira after all?

566
00:50:24,729 --> 00:50:26,271
N-No way!

567
00:50:27,065 --> 00:50:29,483
Chigira-kun is someone
from above the clouds,

568
00:50:29,609 --> 00:50:31,360
he lives in a different world.

569
00:50:31,945 --> 00:50:33,095
But only Chigira-kun...

570
00:50:35,907 --> 00:50:38,909
I will absolutely not
fall for Chigira-kun.

571
00:50:45,458 --> 00:50:47,710
Wait, Miss Wizard, there's
something I need to talk about.

572
00:50:47,794 --> 00:50:48,919
Don't touch her..

573
00:50:55,552 --> 00:50:56,760
Chigira-kun?

574
00:51:00,223 --> 00:51:02,224
What kind of relationship do you two have?

575
00:51:02,308 --> 00:51:04,018
You're not dating. Right?

576
00:51:04,227 --> 00:51:05,894
It's none of your business.

577
00:51:19,743 --> 00:51:21,201
I don't understand.

578
00:51:29,210 --> 00:51:30,669
Chigira-kun!

579
00:51:34,048 --> 00:51:35,675
Hanasaki-san is waiting.

580
00:51:35,759 --> 00:51:37,342
Yeah, I got it.

581
00:51:50,899 --> 00:51:51,815
Thank you.

582
00:52:04,788 --> 00:52:05,829
That's right.

583
00:52:12,796 --> 00:52:15,839
Unrequited love isn't just fun.

584
00:52:23,759 --> 00:52:26,433
[I washed it.]

585
00:52:28,520 --> 00:52:29,686
It's painful.

586
00:52:46,538 --> 00:52:50,415
Hmm, it's a relationship you
can't talk about with others?

587
00:52:51,668 --> 00:52:53,018
What are you talking about?

588
00:53:06,599 --> 00:53:10,352
I've liked you for a long time.

589
00:53:12,897 --> 00:53:14,523
Go out with me.

590
00:53:19,737 --> 00:53:23,407
What is this one-sided
love game? It's stupid.

591
00:53:25,869 --> 00:53:28,954
Aren't you just being played by Chigira?

592
00:53:29,038 --> 00:53:33,500
Chigira-kun is just trying to
cheer me up after my heartbreak.

593
00:53:35,044 --> 00:53:37,671
Please, Tezuka-kun, don't
tell anyone else about this.

594
00:53:37,755 --> 00:53:40,340
It would bother Chigira-kun too much.

595
00:53:40,425 --> 00:53:42,968
If your goal is to heal from heartbreak,

596
00:53:43,094 --> 00:53:45,167
So it doesn't matter
if the other person in

597
00:53:45,251 --> 00:53:47,301
this "pretend game"
is not Chigira, right?

598
00:53:49,058 --> 00:53:49,975
Huh?

599
00:54:02,488 --> 00:54:03,655
Miss Wizard...

600
00:54:04,908 --> 00:54:06,758
Play the one-sided love game with me.

601
00:54:12,957 --> 00:54:14,791
Why would you say that?

602
00:54:16,252 --> 00:54:16,710
That's...

603
00:54:16,794 --> 00:54:18,795
Are you making fun of me?

604
00:54:27,013 --> 00:54:28,138
Anyway,

605
00:54:29,599 --> 00:54:31,600
please keep this a secret.

606
00:54:34,771 --> 00:54:36,104
I beg you.

607
00:54:54,832 --> 00:54:56,458
It's because I like you!

608
00:55:00,171 --> 00:55:02,714
I don't want to see you looking so sad.

609
00:55:04,634 --> 00:55:06,844
Even if you do this with Chigira,

610
00:55:06,928 --> 00:55:09,028
the one who will get
hurt is you, isn't it?

611
00:55:13,851 --> 00:55:15,143
I'm...

612
00:55:16,020 --> 00:55:18,689
genuinely worried about you.

613
00:55:27,699 --> 00:55:28,699
I'm sorry.

614
00:56:01,858 --> 00:56:04,234
What? A consultation?

615
00:56:05,987 --> 00:56:07,446
Um...

616
00:56:08,948 --> 00:56:10,490
About that...

617
00:56:10,575 --> 00:56:11,908
About Chigira?

618
00:56:12,452 --> 00:56:13,494
Huh?

619
00:56:13,578 --> 00:56:17,122
So, Maya's crush is really Chigira, huh?

620
00:56:17,457 --> 00:56:18,874
Chika-chan...

621
00:56:20,001 --> 00:56:20,960
Are you Psychic?

622
00:56:21,044 --> 00:56:23,754
No, no, it's obvious!

623
00:56:24,297 --> 00:56:26,340
Is that what you wanted to talk about?

624
00:56:26,507 --> 00:56:28,509
No, it's just that...

625
00:56:28,593 --> 00:56:30,386
Something unexpected happened,

626
00:56:30,470 --> 00:56:32,570
and I feel like my
head's going to explode.

627
00:56:32,722 --> 00:56:34,431
I don't really understand,

628
00:56:34,515 --> 00:56:37,142
but why does it have to
be Chigira of all people?

629
00:56:37,477 --> 00:56:39,728
This is going to stir up Tezuka again.

630
00:56:42,440 --> 00:56:43,732
What do you mean?

631
00:56:48,404 --> 00:56:52,991
Hey, did something happen between
Chigira-kun and Tezuka-kun in the past?

632
00:56:54,077 --> 00:56:57,537
Chika-chan, weren't you in the
same middle school as them?

633
00:56:58,623 --> 00:57:01,666
Please tell me.

634
00:57:08,007 --> 00:57:09,508
Those two...

635
00:57:09,592 --> 00:57:12,803
I recruited Chigira Sui-kun
from the soccer team!

636
00:57:15,181 --> 00:57:18,475
He was so persistent, I
had no choice but to transfer.

637
00:57:18,559 --> 00:57:20,143
Come on, stop it.

638
00:57:21,354 --> 00:57:24,481
With him, our track and
field team is the strongest.

639
00:57:28,945 --> 00:57:30,153
What's the matter?

640
00:57:38,704 --> 00:57:40,831
At first, they really got along well.

641
00:57:42,458 --> 00:57:43,417
But...

642
00:57:48,089 --> 00:57:51,508
Chigira quickly surpassed Tezuka's time.

643
00:58:04,105 --> 00:58:05,805
What do you mean, you're quitting?

644
00:58:06,399 --> 00:58:08,859
Shut up, it doesn't matter.

645
00:58:08,943 --> 00:58:09,568
Wait a minute.

646
00:58:09,652 --> 00:58:11,027
Don't touch me!

647
00:58:12,947 --> 00:58:15,074
Always acting calm and handling everything skillfully...

648
00:58:15,158 --> 00:58:17,785
Always acting calm and
handling everything skillfully...

649
00:58:17,869 --> 00:58:20,370
When I look at your face, it irritates me.

650
00:58:34,635 --> 00:58:36,785
I think he must have
been really frustrated.

651
00:58:38,806 --> 00:58:40,182
For him...

652
00:58:41,559 --> 00:58:43,477
all he had was track and field.

653
00:59:03,122 --> 00:59:05,457
So, you were running since morning?

654
00:59:05,541 --> 00:59:08,251
Impressive how you keep
doing it without getting tired.

655
00:59:14,717 --> 00:59:17,928
Yesterday, I hugged Maya Kisaragi.

656
00:59:34,612 --> 00:59:36,988
Sorry, my legs are long.

657
00:59:38,199 --> 00:59:39,866
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

658
00:59:40,660 --> 00:59:42,494
Don't get close to Maya.

659
00:59:43,329 --> 00:59:46,331
You too, what's with
that one-sided love game?

660
00:59:47,208 --> 00:59:49,251
It's just nonsense,
are you kindergartners?

661
00:59:49,335 --> 00:59:50,586
It's none of your business.

662
00:59:50,670 --> 00:59:51,962
It does concern me!

663
00:59:54,048 --> 00:59:56,341
If you hurt her, I won't
forgive you, seriously.

664
00:59:56,425 --> 00:59:57,759
Same goes for you.

665
00:59:57,843 --> 01:00:00,053
If you hurt Maya, I won't forgive you.

666
01:00:24,245 --> 01:00:27,038
What happened between
Tezuka and you yesterday?

667
01:00:31,252 --> 01:00:34,504
Is it true that Tezuka hugged you?

668
01:00:36,340 --> 01:00:38,049
Well, um...

669
01:00:38,384 --> 01:00:40,302
I wonder how it was...

670
01:00:53,149 --> 01:00:54,441
Chigira-kun?

671
01:01:06,454 --> 01:01:07,662
Disinfection.

672
01:01:09,081 --> 01:01:11,333
Don't let any other guy touch you.

673
01:01:28,726 --> 01:01:30,518
Regarding Hanasaki-san,

674
01:01:32,188 --> 01:01:34,648
I don't plan on dating anyone right now.

675
01:01:35,566 --> 01:01:36,900
Because I have Maya.

676
01:01:41,906 --> 01:01:45,033
I don't want to end this
one-sided love game

677
01:01:47,703 --> 01:01:49,913
until Maya's wounds are properly healed.

678
01:01:57,421 --> 01:01:59,255
One-sided love game...

679
01:02:09,016 --> 01:02:10,058
What if...

680
01:02:13,979 --> 01:02:17,690
What if I say the wounds have been healed?

681
01:02:18,234 --> 01:02:19,192
Huh?

682
01:02:21,529 --> 01:02:23,321
The game will be over.

683
01:02:23,948 --> 01:02:27,158
We're just going back to
how things were, nothing more.

684
01:02:28,702 --> 01:02:30,453
The hug from earlier,

685
01:02:31,122 --> 01:02:32,372
also the kiss,

686
01:02:34,041 --> 01:02:35,708
it was all just a "game."

687
01:02:37,253 --> 01:02:38,712
It wasn't real.

688
01:02:40,047 --> 01:02:41,297
Maya?

689
01:02:45,136 --> 01:02:49,097
And yet, I find myself
elated and then depressed.

690
01:02:52,601 --> 01:02:54,686
Being with you right now, Chigira-kun...

691
01:02:56,272 --> 01:02:57,856
is painful.

692
01:03:12,037 --> 01:03:15,540
I'm sorry. What am I saying?

693
01:03:19,879 --> 01:03:21,922
Huh! Hey, isn't that Chigichigi?

694
01:03:22,006 --> 01:03:24,466
Huh? Oh, really!

695
01:03:27,970 --> 01:03:29,053
Maya!

696
01:03:32,141 --> 01:03:33,224
Maya!

697
01:04:11,764 --> 01:04:13,348
Chigira-kun?

698
01:04:16,060 --> 01:04:17,727
Chigira-kun.

699
01:04:18,604 --> 01:04:20,188
Chigira-kun!

700
01:04:34,370 --> 01:04:35,537
Maya!

701
01:04:37,206 --> 01:04:38,373
Chika-chan...

702
01:04:39,375 --> 01:04:40,792
How's Chigira?!

703
01:04:41,460 --> 01:04:42,835
He's in the Treatment Room.

704
01:04:45,005 --> 01:04:47,006
He might have sprained his ligament.

705
01:04:48,259 --> 01:04:49,092
Huh?

706
01:04:52,763 --> 01:04:54,430
It's my fault.

707
01:04:58,102 --> 01:05:00,937
In truth. I have overwritten
my feelings already.

708
01:05:07,319 --> 01:05:09,821
But I wanted to be with Chigira-kun,

709
01:05:13,158 --> 01:05:14,868
so I relied on his kindness,

710
01:05:17,746 --> 01:05:20,081
and hid my true feelings.

711
01:05:23,919 --> 01:05:25,962
So I guess I'm being punished...

712
01:06:14,428 --> 01:06:16,721
Huh? Is Chigichigi's injury that bad?

713
01:06:16,889 --> 01:06:18,431
It depends on his rehabilitation. But..

714
01:06:18,515 --> 01:06:20,965
He probably won't make it
to the Kanto Tournament.

715
01:06:21,060 --> 01:06:22,727
Eh, seriously?

716
01:06:22,895 --> 01:06:25,188
Sui practiced so hard.

717
01:06:25,272 --> 01:06:26,982
It's true, right?

718
01:06:27,066 --> 01:06:28,859
Eh, seriously... I
wonder if he'll be okay.

719
01:06:28,943 --> 01:06:30,318
What a disaster...

720
01:07:54,319 --> 01:07:55,862
I'll open it a bit more, okay?

721
01:08:16,216 --> 01:08:18,426
Put more effort into it, more power.

722
01:08:22,556 --> 01:08:24,057
Let's do one more round..

723
01:08:24,266 --> 01:08:25,099
Yes.

724
01:08:33,650 --> 01:08:34,692
Okay!

725
01:09:15,150 --> 01:09:16,901
Okay, here it goes.

726
01:09:18,112 --> 01:09:19,320
Ouch...

727
01:09:24,660 --> 01:09:25,993
It hurts...

728
01:09:30,165 --> 01:09:31,499
Tezuka-kun...

729
01:09:32,960 --> 01:09:36,060
You were doing a hundred-day
pilgrimage for Chigira-kun's sake?

730
01:09:36,672 --> 01:09:40,091
Even if you don't do that,
he'll come back soon anyway.

731
01:09:40,425 --> 01:09:41,875
That's the kind of guy he is.

732
01:09:44,471 --> 01:09:46,848
Tezuka, about the other day...

733
01:09:46,932 --> 01:09:48,975
Ah, it's okay, forget about that story.

734
01:09:49,977 --> 01:09:53,527
Anyway, you're probably thinking
about Chigichigi right now, aren't you?

735
01:09:55,816 --> 01:09:59,402
Tezuka-kun, do you dislike Chigira-kun?

736
01:10:00,112 --> 01:10:01,988
Huh? Why are you suddenly asking?

737
01:10:02,489 --> 01:10:05,533
Sorry, I heard it from Chika-chan.

738
01:10:05,868 --> 01:10:06,909
Well...

739
01:10:08,078 --> 01:10:09,370
About track and field...

740
01:10:10,330 --> 01:10:11,831
That girl.

741
01:10:13,959 --> 01:10:17,461
It's just like an
unrequited love, isn't it?

742
01:10:18,630 --> 01:10:19,714
Huh?

743
01:10:20,883 --> 01:10:23,593
The feeling of chasing something
that you can never reach,

744
01:10:23,677 --> 01:10:25,386
no matter how hard you try.

745
01:10:26,388 --> 01:10:27,488
I understand that too.

746
01:10:30,100 --> 01:10:32,602
The feeling of being hurt.

747
01:10:32,686 --> 01:10:35,230
Hating everything.

748
01:10:35,314 --> 01:10:36,814
And wanting to give up.

749
01:10:42,529 --> 01:10:44,280
But if you really hate it,

750
01:10:45,240 --> 01:10:47,190
I don't think you would chase after it.

751
01:10:48,035 --> 01:10:49,243
Tezuka-kun,

752
01:10:50,162 --> 01:10:52,246
you really like Chigira-kun, don't you?

753
01:11:14,811 --> 01:11:17,355
As expected of Miss
Wizard, you are the best.

754
01:11:18,315 --> 01:11:20,942
I like Chigira-kun...

755
01:11:39,169 --> 01:11:40,419
Tezuka-kun?

756
01:11:51,098 --> 01:11:54,558
Miss Wizard, what will you do from now on?

757
01:12:07,322 --> 01:12:08,447
As for me...

758
01:12:21,431 --> 01:12:23,081
-I had fun too.
-I'll take good care of the keychain!

759
01:12:23,166 --> 01:12:25,118
-Yeah.
-Sorry.
-It's not your fault, Maya.

760
01:12:34,426 --> 01:12:38,599
[I want to see you.]

761
01:12:42,816 --> 01:12:44,816
Being with you right now, Chigira-kun...

762
01:12:46,403 --> 01:12:47,862
is painful.

763
01:13:18,727 --> 01:13:19,852
Maya...

764
01:13:28,111 --> 01:13:31,280
I was worried because
you didn't contact much.

765
01:13:31,948 --> 01:13:32,990
I'm sorry.

766
01:13:34,451 --> 01:13:36,160
How are your injuries?

767
01:13:36,620 --> 01:13:38,204
It's recovering smoothly.

768
01:13:39,289 --> 01:13:42,166
That's why I decided to
participate in the tournament.

769
01:13:42,918 --> 01:13:43,751
Huh?

770
01:13:44,378 --> 01:13:45,544
Is it okay?

771
01:13:45,754 --> 01:13:46,754
It's okay.

772
01:13:47,589 --> 01:13:50,508
So, Maya, you don't have to worry anymore.

773
01:13:51,510 --> 01:13:52,635
The tournament

774
01:13:53,720 --> 01:13:55,520
I want you to come and cheer for me.

775
01:14:03,271 --> 01:14:06,524
You're always kind, Chigira-kun.

776
01:14:09,861 --> 01:14:13,739
You suddenly appeared when I was down,

777
01:14:14,199 --> 01:14:16,450
and said the words I  need the most.

778
01:14:22,499 --> 01:14:26,335
But let's put an end to this
one-sided love game, okay?

779
01:14:27,212 --> 01:14:28,129
Huh?

780
01:14:30,841 --> 01:14:32,550
Thanks to you, Chigira-kun,

781
01:14:32,634 --> 01:14:35,034
the pain of my heartbreak
is completely gone now!

782
01:14:58,702 --> 01:15:02,580
I'm sorry I said it was painful!

783
01:15:06,042 --> 01:15:07,293
I had fun.

784
01:15:08,962 --> 01:15:10,754
It was the best time ever.

785
01:15:14,259 --> 01:15:16,802
Are you really okay now?

786
01:16:11,316 --> 01:16:13,484
Yes, I'm really fine now.

787
01:16:15,111 --> 01:16:16,695
Thank you for today.

788
01:16:19,991 --> 01:16:21,116
Well then.

789
01:16:28,625 --> 01:16:29,625
Maya...

790
01:16:31,503 --> 01:16:33,921
Good luck in the tournament.

791
01:17:38,778 --> 01:17:39,987
Why...

792
01:17:48,997 --> 01:17:51,797
The reason Chigira-kun
become so fond of track and field.

793
01:17:52,792 --> 01:17:54,960
Maybe it's because of your influence.

794
01:17:55,420 --> 01:17:56,253
Huh?

795
01:17:57,130 --> 01:17:58,505
Maya mentioned that.

796
01:17:58,840 --> 01:18:02,134
"To love the things your beloved loves."

797
01:18:03,345 --> 01:18:06,545
Isn't it just the way things are
in the world of unrequited love?

798
01:18:45,303 --> 01:18:47,554
I wonder if Chigichigi can win?

799
01:18:48,264 --> 01:18:50,140
He didn't practice enough.

800
01:18:51,059 --> 01:18:53,435
It's okay, I'm here for him.

801
01:18:56,773 --> 01:18:59,483
Are you making that "Didn't
you just got dumped?" face?

802
01:18:59,692 --> 01:19:03,320
I've decided I'm going to
be Sui's number one fan!

803
01:19:06,282 --> 01:19:07,491
That's great.

804
01:19:08,785 --> 01:19:10,703
Hold on a second.

805
01:19:10,787 --> 01:19:11,579
